I confess.
When I write about freedoms lost, I don&rsquo;t itemize the freedoms. I don&rsquo;t feel too bad, though, because almost no one does. Itemizing sucks.
First, it&rsquo;s hard work. &ldquo;Losing freedom,&rdquo; takes about three seconds to type and less time to read. Listing freedoms,on the other hand, takes that much time just to highlight all the freedoms and click the un-ordered list button. God forbid I find myself working in straight HTML and have to hand-type &quot;
